			Managing Director, Global Head of Client Service and Marketing, CenterSquare
		












CenterSquare Investment Management Holdings, Inc. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of The Bank of New York Mellon Corporation. CenterSquare Investment Management, Inc. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of CenterSquare Investment Management Holdings, Inc. 
